atoms.title: Before You Start
atoms.text:
### Introduction
In this lesson, we will focus on the modeling part of the QMV process in more depth.

Given that you have already had some background in machine learning, we highlight non-parametric statistical models as the focus of this lesson. 

The techniques we will cover in this lesson will carry over to parametric models, mathematical models and machine learning models. 
  
### Downloads
This [download link](https://www.udacity.com/api/nodes/3605708596/supplemental_media/lesson-3-fileszip/download) contains the files that you need to follow along Rishi in lesson 3.
